SUMMARY:Land Development Code Update Interactive Community Meeting
LOCATION:Ragan Park Community Center 1200 East Lake Avenue Tampa \, FL 336
 05 United States
DESCRIPTION:Tampa is growing\, and the rules that guide how our city devel
 ops are evolving too. Join us for an interactive community meeting on Tamp
 a Forward\, where youll learn what the Land Development Code is\, why it m
 atters\, and how it impacts your neighborhood. Come ask questions\, share 
 your perspective\, and be part of the conversation shaping Tampas next cha
 pter. Learn more at: tampa.govTampaForward In accordance with the American
 s with Disabilities Act (ADA) and Section 286.26\, Florida Statutes\, pers
 ons with disabilities needing a reasonable accommodation should contact th
 e City of Tampas ADA Coordinator. The ADA Coordinator may be contacted by 
