SUMMARY:Clean Comedy Showcase
LOCATION:811 E 7th Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Looking for an afternoon of comedy you can simply enjoy? Join 
 us for a clean\, supportive comedy experience featuring local comics worki
 ng on material you can feel comfortable sharing with your friends. Sunday\
 , June 7 4:005:30 PM The Commodore  Ybor 5 tickets  Free parking  No drink
  minimum A relaxed Sunday crowd. Clean material. Plenty of laughs. Tweet G
 ame Finale is a crowd favorite Adults and teens welcome. Supporting Shower
 Up Were collecting:  New or gently used towels (no stains or rips)  Extra 
 toothbrushes\, toothpaste\, floss\, and toiletries Comedy so clean we brin
 g towels. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/191091
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191091
