SUMMARY:Tampa Bay Orchid Society to Host Orchid Auction Featuring More Tha
 n 250 Plants on June 20
LOCATION:501 S Dale Mabry Hwy. Tampa \, FL 33609 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Tampa Bay Orchid Society will host its upcoming orchid auc
 tion on June 20\, 2026\, at Good Shepherd Lutheran Church\, offering plant
  enthusiasts and collectors the opportunity to bid on more than 250 orchid
 s and related items. Experienced and favored by all\, auctioneer Laura New
 ton is both entertaining and informative. Come for a good time and leave w
 ith beautiful plants. The auction will feature a wide selection of plants 
 for both experienced growers and those new to orchid collecting. Attendees
  will have the chance to browse and bid on a diverse assortment of orchids
 \, including unique varieties and plants suitable for a range of growing c
 onditions. Plant preview starts at 9:30 am. Auction begins at 10:00 am. Cr
 edit cards are accepted. Were excited to welcome longtime orchid growers a
 s well as people discovering orchids for the first time\, said a represent
 ative of the Tampa Bay Orchid Society. With more than 250 plants available
 \, there will be opportunities for attendees to find something special to 
 add to their collections. Plant preview starts at 9:30 am. Auction begins 
 at 10:00 am\, credit cards accepted. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/
 node/190801
