SUMMARY:Strong Over 50 Experience at Busch Gardens
LOCATION:10165 N McKinley Dr\, Tampa\, FL 33612 Tampa \, FL 33612 United S
 tates
DESCRIPTION:The Strong Over 50 Busch Gardens Fitness Experience is a free 
 wellness event designed for adults ages 50 focused on helping older adults
  improve strength\, mobility\, energy\, and overall health in a fun and su
 pportive environment. Hosted at Busch Gardens Tampa Bay inside the Gwazi P
 avilion\, the event features instructor-led strength training\, Pilates\, 
 and dance fitness sessions\, wellness vendors\, giveaways\, free breakfast
 \, and access to Busch Gardens after the program. The event brings togethe
 r seniors\, health professionals\, community organizations\, and wellness 
 partners for a high-energy morning centered around healthy aging and activ
 e living. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190361
